<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Question Forum</title>
    <style>
      .body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .card {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .card h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      .card p {
        margin: 10px 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #555;
      }
      .card ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .card ul li {
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/navbar.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <%-include("./components/navbar.ejs")%>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>About Our Question Forum</h2>
          <p>
            Welcome to our Question Forum! This platform is designed to
            facilitate discussions and knowledge sharing among users. Here's
            what you can do:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Post Questions:</strong> Users can create and post
              questions on various topics.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Provide Answers:</strong> Other users can provide answers
              to these questions, fostering a collaborative environment.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Edit Answers:</strong> Users can edit their own answers to
              correct or improve them.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Delete Answers:</strong> Users have the ability to delete
              their own answers if needed.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Our goal is to create a community where users can share knowledge,
            ask questions, and get answers in a supportive environment. Join us
            and contribute to the discussion!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
